title: Dark Souls Remastered Edition-2018 Incl.DLC
description:
DARK SOULS: REMASTERED 2018 + Multiplayer

Re-experience the genre-defining game that started it  all.  
Beautifully  remastered!!
Return to Lordran in  stunning high-definition  detail  running  at
60fps.  Dark  Souls  Remastered includes  the main  game  plus  the
Artorias of the Abyss DLC. 

Key features: -Deep  and  Dark  Universe
-Each End is a New Beginning -Gameplay Richness  and  Possibilities
-Sense of Learning, Mastering and Accomplishment -The  Way  of  the
Multiplayer (up to 6 players with dedicated servers)


Support the Devs!!

ScreenShots: store.steampowered.com/app/570940
